INSERT INTO Orders (
	Ordername, 
	Notes, 
	Address, 
	ContactName, 
	PhoneEmail, 
	Date, 
	ShipmentID, 
	OrderSize, 
	Product1, Price1, 
	Product2, Price2, 
	Product3, Price3, 
	Product4, Price4, 
	Product5, Price5)
VALUES (
		'{{CreateOrderForm.data.OrderIn}}',
	  '{{CreateOrderForm.data.OrderNotesIn}}',
	  '{{CreateOrderForm.data.AddressIn}}',
	  '{{CreateOrderForm.data.ContactNameIn}}',
	  '{{CreateOrderForm.data.ContactPhoneEmailIn}}',
	  '{{new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0]}}',
	  '{{CreateOrderForm.data.ShipmentIDC}}',
	  '{{CreateOrderForm.data.OrderSizeIn}}',
	  '{{CreateOrderForm.data.Product1}}',
	  '{{CreateOrderForm.data.Price1}}',
	  '{{CreateOrderForm.data.Product2}}',
	  '{{CreateOrderForm.data.Price2}}',
	  '{{CreateOrderForm.data.Product3}}',
	  '{{CreateOrderForm.data.Price3}}',
	  '{{CreateOrderForm.data.Product4}}',
	  '{{CreateOrderForm.data.Price4}}',
	  '{{CreateOrderForm.data.Product5}}',
	  '{{CreateOrderForm.data.Price5}}');
